---
import '../styles/tokens.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | eixo.design</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy policy for eixo.design — how we handle your data." />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/eixo-favicon.png" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <a href="/">
        <img src="/assets/images/eixo-logo-white.png" alt="eixo.design" />
      </a>
      <a href="/">Back to site</a>
    </header>

    <main>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>eixo.design is a UX design consultancy based in Amsterdam, the Netherlands, operated by Natalia Arsand. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data.</p>

      <h2>What data we collect</h2>
      <h3>Contact form</h3>
      <p>When you submit our contact form, we collect your name, email address, company name (optional), and your message. This data is sent to our email and used solely to respond to your inquiry. We do not store form submissions in a database.</p>

      <h3>Analytics</h3>
      <p>With your consent, we use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. This collects anonymised data such as pages visited and time on site. No personally identifiable information is collected.</p>

      <h2>How we use your data</h2>
      <p>We use the information you provide to respond to your inquiry, discuss potential collaboration, and improve our services. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties.</p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>Contact form submissions are retained in our email for as long as necessary to manage the professional relationship. You can request deletion at any time.</p>

      <h2>Your rights under GDPR</h2>
      <p>Under the GDPR / AVG, you have the right to access, correct, delete, restrict, or port your personal data. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@eixo.design">hello@eixo.design</a>.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>Our site uses cookies from Google Analytics, loaded only after your consent. No advertising or tracking cookies are used. You can withdraw consent at any time.</p>

      <h2>Third-party services</h2>
      <p>We use Google Analytics (consent-based analytics), Cloudflare (hosting), Brevo (email delivery), and Google Fonts (typography).</p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date.</p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@eixo.design">hello@eixo.design</a>.</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--white-a8);
  }

  header img {
    height: 20px;
    width: auto;
  }

  header a {
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  header a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  main {
    max-width: var(--content-text);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-3);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  .meta {
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: var(--space-5) 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
